snippet.title: Kirby: Wacky Episode (Kirby Fangame Playthrough)
snippet.description:
Kirby: Wacky Episode is a great Kirby fangame made by AlexAugerDev. It's relatively short but has a story mode and some extra content. With all of the depth the gameplay has, which is its best part, this game is a must-play.

Link: https://alexaugerdev.itch.io/kirby-wacky-episode

0:00 Intro
0:30 Story Mode: Green Greens
4:24 Story Mode: Cloudbed Castle
10:25 Story Mode: Rainbow Islands
17:04 Story Mode: Ability Room & Credits
18:06 Story Mode: Extra Bosses
21:15 Kirby Quick
27:05 Virus Rush
35:57 The Arena
42:01 Outro
